snippet.title: CUBE RAILWAY (TEASER)
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3082610/Cube_Railway__Puzzle/

Cube Railway is a puzzle game where players must strategically fit blocks to complete a railway track and set the train in motion. Reach the next level by correctly placing the cubes within the designated spots on the track.
